<para><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis>System:</emphasis></emphasis> networks and large-scale "systems of systems"</para>
<para><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis>Mission:</emphasis></emphasis> meeting established high-level requirements/goals</para>
<para><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis>Critical:</emphasis></emphasis> critical factor specified or implied by mission requirements</para>
