<para><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis>Attacks:</emphasis></emphasis> orchestrated by an intelligent adversary</para>
<para><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis>Failures:</emphasis></emphasis> deficiencies in elements on which the system depends</para>
<para><emphasis role="bold"><emphasis>Accidents:</emphasis></emphasis> randomly occurring events</para>
</entry>
