<entry valign="top">
<para><emphasis role="bold">Automation</emphasis></para>
<para>- Bar codes, optical scanners, web-tracking, computerized parsing, etc.</para>
<para><emphasis role="bold">Fault Tolerance</emphasis></para>
<para>- Alternate flights/hubs, substitute letter-carriers, inter-post office communication</para>
<para><emphasis role="bold">Management</emphasis></para>
<para>- Extensive training program, personnel accountability, infusion of pride, etc.</para>
